{"info": {"author": "lihe", "author_email": "imanux@sina.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8"], "description": "# sgr-ansi\n\nawesome SGR ANSI colorful text interface in terminal\n\n> full supported in python3.7+, macosx\n\n## awesome colorful text\n\n![colorful usage](docs/images/usage.png)\n\n![colorful demo1](docs/images/demo1.png)\n\n![colorful demo2](docs/images/demo2.png)\n\n## install\n\n```shell\npip install sgr-ansi\n```\n\n## usage\n\nBeware of two rules:\n- styles require **alphabet order**\n- styles go before colors\n\nabout styles, you can use as many as possible, but colors only the last two will take effect\n\nso like `BDISUkrgybmcw`, all `BDISU` will take effect, but for colors only `cw: cyan on white` will take effect\n\n### styles/colors supported\n\n> styles\n\nB: bold, D: dimmed, I: italic, S: strike_through, U: underlined\n\n> colors\n\nk: black, r: red, g: green, y: yellow b: blue, m: magenta, c: cyan, w: white\n\n\n```python\nimport sgr_ansi as echo\n\necho.BIg()\necho.BIg('I love you 3 thousand times')\n```\n\n### chained call\n\n```python\nfrom sgr_ansi import Chain\n\nChain().BIy('Yep,').BIUb(\n    'How do you like this?'\n).Bm('\\n\\t[\u2714]').BUg('1.').Bg('Y: yes.').Bm('\\n\\t[\u2718]').BUr('2.').Br('N: not.').show()\n```\n\n![colorful chain](docs/images/chain.png)\n\n## run demo\n\n> just run `sgransi` to check all available styles\n\n```sh\n# after installed sgr_ansi, cli sgransi is available\nsgransi -h\n```\n\n\n", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/coghost/sgr-ansi", "keywords": "sgr,ansi,colorful,vivid,awesome,terminal", "license": "GPL", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "sgr-ansi", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/sgr-ansi/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/sgr-ansi/", "project_urls": {"Bug Reports": "https://github.com/coghost/sgr-ansi/issues", "Homepage": "https://github.com/coghost/sgr-ansi", "Source": "https://github.com/coghost/sgr-ansi"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/sgr-ansi/0.0.4/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": ">=3.7", "summary": "awesome ansi8 colorful text interface in terminal", "version": "0.0.4", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>sgr-ansi</h1>\n<p>awesome SGR ANSI colorful text interface in terminal</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>full supported in python3.7+, macosx</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>awesome colorful text</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"colorful usage\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/a81c2498d5c7b0d9909b0d1fb52a50cfbadaf747/646f63732f696d616765732f75736167652e706e67\"></p>\n<p><img alt=\"colorful demo1\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/bcd9310fa394e1bd89fbe4a4093880968d09230c/646f63732f696d616765732f64656d6f312e706e67\"></p>\n<p><img alt=\"colorful demo2\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/91afbff9eb490d1358445594ad6117488bf79081/646f63732f696d616765732f64656d6f322e706e67\"></p>\n<h2>install</h2>\n<pre>pip install sgr-ansi\n</pre>\n<h2>usage</h2>\n<p>Beware of two rules:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>styles require <strong>alphabet order</strong></li>\n<li>styles go before colors</li>\n</ul>\n<p>about styles, you can use as many as possible, but colors only the last two will take effect</p>\n<p>so like <code>BDISUkrgybmcw</code>, all <code>BDISU</code> will take effect, but for colors only <code>cw: cyan on white</code> will take effect</p>\n<h3>styles/colors supported</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>styles</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>B: bold, D: dimmed, I: italic, S: strike_through, U: underlined</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>colors</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>k: black, r: red, g: green, y: yellow b: blue, m: magenta, c: cyan, w: white</p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">sgr_ansi</span> <span class=\"k\">as</span> <span class=\"nn\">echo</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">echo</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">BIg</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"n\">echo</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">BIg</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'I love you 3 thousand times'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<h3>chained call</h3>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">sgr_ansi</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Chain</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">Chain</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">BIy</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'Yep,'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">BIUb</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"s1\">'How do you like this?'</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Bm</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'</span><span class=\"se\">\\n\\t</span><span class=\"s1\">[\u2714]'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">BUg</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'1.'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Bg</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'Y: yes.'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Bm</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'</span><span class=\"se\">\\n\\t</span><span class=\"s1\">[\u2718]'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">BUr</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'2.'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Br</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'N: not.'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">show</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n</pre>\n<p><img alt=\"colorful chain\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/a0901cd59d330b445672e147ec86196df6219545/646f63732f696d616765732f636861696e2e706e67\"></p>\n<h2>run demo</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>just run <code>sgransi</code> to check all available styles</p>\n</blockquote>\n<pre><span class=\"c1\"># after installed sgr_ansi, cli sgransi is available</span>\nsgransi -h\n</pre>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 7005134, "releases": {"0.0.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "5980eb35d226c5505f5cf3e378dd4cd0", "sha256": "b89b9dcd7107121c5ecad55c692892b8cbd9fbbcfe0cb8d1a360345690ef510a"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "sgr_ansi-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "5980eb35d226c5505f5cf3e378dd4cd0", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": ">=3.7", "size": 21030, "upload_time": "2020-04-05T13:39:05", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-04-05T13:39:05.036873Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/72/ae/79bef5ec5b2c0e28b80e7f2d51c30f98dbc6a2abcf77c03134d406f7fa14/sgr_ansi-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}, {"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "3560fb9b5fd81f9f01b680b922760e64", "sha256": "dfa87602f9e864736605fa725d3493c5b4fa50bbc84a3ca3e22418ddae0b9724"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "sgr-ansi-0.0.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "3560fb9b5fd81f9f01b680b922760e64", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": ">=3.7", "size": 9254, "upload_time": "2020-04-05T13:39:07", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-04-05T13:39:07.385104Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/45/11/ca6c6b8886ec177b330bd46fd7117c2aeec11cb142394e5827e0477de113/sgr-ansi-0.0.1.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.0.2": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "c149a4ff870f16bcd1fce0fbf8e8bf7e", "sha256": "356a34b163ebe1414abe93295047ab6f0665db10fa7102a66da217f698dabac2"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "sgr_ansi-0.0.2-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "c149a4ff870f16bcd1fce0fbf8e8bf7e", "packagetype": "bdist